86
00:05:28,398 --> 00:05:30,764
This is gonna be
the best Christmas ever.

87
00:05:30,834 --> 00:05:33,200
And we're going to do it together,
so come on.

88
00:05:57,527 --> 00:06:00,519
Everything looks so good!

89
00:06:00,597 --> 00:06:02,189
Nice job, honey.

90
00:06:02,265 --> 00:06:04,597
Well, we all did it together.

91
00:06:04,668 --> 00:06:08,399
Now what would the perfect Christmas
be without a Christmas story?

92
00:06:09,806 --> 00:06:14,106
'Twas the night before Christmas
and all through the house

93
00:06:14,177 --> 00:06:17,578
Not a creature was stirring...
What?

94
00:06:17,648 --> 00:06:20,276
- Merry Christmas, Shrek!
- Oh, not you!

95
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:22,477
We're here to smother you
with Christmas love!

96
00:06:22,552 --> 00:06:25,248
Absolutely not!
Bad Donkey! Go home!

97
00:06:25,322 --> 00:06:27,688
How are you gonna have
Christmas without family?

98
00:06:27,758 --> 00:06:29,692
- Seasons greeting!
- Happy Holidays!

99
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,694
- Merry Christmas!
- A nice surprise!

100
00:06:31,762 --> 00:06:33,195
Oh, yeah.

101
00:06:36,299 --> 00:06:39,860
OK, I will assume the position.

102
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:47,440
