Hey, baby, you mind?

107
00:07:02,259 --> 00:07:04,955
- Oh, boy!
- This way, gents.

108
00:07:05,629 --> 00:07:06,926
That was our supper!

109
00:07:08,465 --> 00:07:09,762
Hey!

110
00:07:11,902 --> 00:07:15,065
Did you hurt yourself
