But what? This is not the
kind of Christmas I had in mind.

120
00:07:55,278 --> 00:07:58,714
They're our friends, Shrek.
They all mean well.

121
00:07:58,782 --> 00:08:01,774
- How many babies did Fiona have?
- She has babies?

122
00:08:01,852 --> 00:08:04,286
- I don't know.
- I better get back to the house.

123
00:08:04,354 --> 00:08:06,379
Surprised we have
a house to go back to.

124
00:08:06,456 --> 00:08:09,914
- Are you coming?
- I can hardly wait.

125
00:08:09,993 --> 00:08:11,824
