126
00:08:20,170 --> 00:08:21,398
Look at him go!

127
00:08:21,471 --> 00:08:23,371
Excuse me! Excuse me!

128
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,169
Excuse you for what?

129
00:08:25,242 --> 00:08:28,234
