142
00:09:12,155 --> 00:09:14,146
- I'm the best teller ever!
- Donkey...

143
00:09:14,224 --> 00:09:15,782
I got it committed
to memorization!

144
00:09:15,859 --> 00:09:17,827
- Gather round!
- Donkey! Wait!

145
00:09:17,894 --> 00:09:20,328
I'm supposed to tell
the Christmas story.

146
00:09:20,397 --> 00:09:23,389
'Twas the night before Christmas
and I spent all the day

147
00:09:23,466 --> 00:09:26,333
Finishin' up on my Christmas display

148
00:09:26,403 --> 00:09:28,997
Now, missin' all this
would be nothin' but tragic

149
00:09:29,072 --> 00:09:31,836
So just follow me
and I'll show you the magic

150
00:09:31,908 --> 00:09:34,069
Now, out in the yard
in a glorious clutter

151
00:09:34,144 --> 00:09:36,977
Is a spectacle there that'll
make your heart flutter

152
00:09:37,047 --> 00:09:39,641
With 20-foot cheese balls
and a big eggnog fountain

153
00:09:39,716 --> 00:09:42,742
And yodelin' elves
on an ambrosia mountain

154
00:09:42,819 --> 00:09:45,344
A stage where acrobats
jump, leap and prance

155
00:09:45,422 --> 00:09:48,516
And honor the day
through interpretive dance

156
00:09:49,392 --> 00:09:51,758
But just when you think
the display is complete

157
00:09:51,828 --> 00:09:54,422
The Christmas parade
comes right down the street

158
00:09:54,497 --> 00:09:56,931
With holiday floats
all in silver and blue

159
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:00,026
With sugarplum fairies
and a reindeer or two

160
00:10:00,103 --> 00:10:02,833
There's a baton-twirlin'
snowman all happy and perky

161
00:10:02,906 --> 00:10:05,807
Magical peacocks
and a dancin' roast turkey

162
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:12,644
And right when you think
that you've just seen it all

163
00:10:12,716 --> 00:10:16,550
