The Santa I know
was a hot Latin cat

176
00:10:57,861 --> 00:11:01,854
He was dressed all in fur
from his head to his paws

177
00:11:01,932 --> 00:11:07,461
And he stood there heroic
A real Santa... Claws

178
00:11:07,537 --> 00:11:10,097
Red are his boots

179
00:11:10,173 --> 00:11:13,006
- And so is his cape
- Olé!

180
00:11:13,076 --> 00:11:17,069
