182
00:11:19,749 --> 00:11:24,243
And there's a cute fuzzy thing
which hangs down from his hat

183
00:11:34,931 --> 00:11:37,525
I have shamed myself.

184
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,830
- Olé!
- All right, everybody,

185
00:11:39,903 --> 00:11:42,770
if you leave now,
you can beat the holiday traffic.

186
00:11:42,839 --> 00:11:45,808
Phooey with all your
sunshine and lollipops!

187
00:11:45,875 --> 00:11:49,311
Where I come from,
Christmas is a nightmare.

188
00:11:51,748 --> 00:11:55,081
'Twas the night before Christmas
and the prettiest sights

189
00:11:55,151 --> 00:11:59,281
Were my sweetheart beside me
in the bright Christmas lights

190
00:11:59,356 --> 00:12:01,051
...until they got home.

191
00:12:01,124 --> 00:12:05,618
When they looked at the car door
handle, and they found a hook!

192
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:10,322
Gingy, cut it out! You're
really givin' me the creeps!

193
