Oh, come on,
I was just teasin'.

194
00:12:13,370 --> 00:12:16,237
Come here, you.

195
00:12:16,306 --> 00:12:18,399
Gingy, I couldn't stay mad at you.

196
00:12:18,475 --> 00:12:20,136
