229
00:14:38,014 --> 00:14:41,609
Shrek, you just kicked
everybody out on Christmas.

230
00:14:41,684 --> 00:14:44,152
Well, that wasn't Christmas.
That was chaos!

231
00:14:44,220 --> 00:14:47,155
Look, I know it didn't
go like you wanted.

232
00:14:47,223 --> 00:14:51,125
What I wanted was a perfect
Christmas for me and my family.

233
00:14:51,194 --> 00:14:53,822
- That was our family.
- You call that a family?

234
00:14:53,897 --> 00:14:56,092
That was a natural disaster!

235
00:14:56,166 --> 00:14:59,101
On Christmas, that's how it
works. Yes, it was crowded.

236
00:14:59,169 --> 00:15:01,228
