- Donkey!

276
00:17:57,146 --> 00:18:00,513
No, none of that.

277
00:18:00,583 --> 00:18:04,019
Ogres don't celebrate Christmas.

278
00:18:04,087 --> 00:18:07,250
Ogres don't celebrate anything.

